OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStorm Dave
OL,6,Fwill bring strong winds this evening
OL,7,Fwith some heavy and blustery spells of
OL,8,Frain at times. The storm will clear in
OL,9,Fthe early hours and winds will ease,
OL,10,Fthough still rather breezy around
OL,11,Fcoasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FSunny spells and scattered
OL,14,Fshowers on Easter Day with lighter
OL,15,Fwinds. Mostly dry by the afternoon but
OL,16,Ffeeling colder than previous days with
OL,17,Fa fresh breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
