OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,6,Fon Monday with good sunny spells.
OL,7,FTurning increasingly warm from
OL,8,FTuesday. Perhaps staying dry on
OL,9,FWednesday but skies clouding over and
OL,10,Fturning less warm.
